                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7715" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1206</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2511 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易见股份舞弊退市，审计“合理保证”能逃脱罪责吗？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">In the Fraudulent Delisting of Easy Visible,Can Auditor Escape Guilt Because of &quot;Reasonable Assurance&quot;?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">翟华明，马小涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易见供应链管理股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务造假；审计程序；审计责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial fraud; Audit procedures; Audit responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被万千股民看好的“区块链第一股”易见股份，曾经是一家与信息技术毫无相关的农业企业，其在新主人的带领下转型成为供应链管理企业后便不断业绩飘红，一路走高。然而这一切终止于2020年的年报难产，经深入立案调查后发现所谓的业绩斐然只是水月镜花的幻影。出人意料的是，在易见股份的六年造假中，天圆全会计师事务所在前五年均出具了标准无保留意见。本案例以易见股份巨额舞弊事件的发展过程为线索，引导学生从审计的角度分析易见股份的财务状况，了解并掌握易见股份财务造假的类型及动因。同时,让学生分析如何识别审计风险。并借助本次事件发生中的点滴细节，引导学生如何运用审计程序识别企业的财务造假行为，理解年报审计中实质性分析程序每个环节的侧重点，从而提高职业警惕性。在了解整个舞弊事件后，让学生对审计责任中的合理保证与独立性要求产生更深层次的理解，同时，思考如何从审计的角度来抑制企业的财务舞弊行为，帮助提高市场对上市公司舞弊行为的监管力度。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Easy Visible Supply Chain Management Company Limited, the &quot;first share of blockchain&quot; favored by millions of investors, used to be an agricultural enterprise that had nothing to do with information technology. Under the leadership of its new owner, Easy Visible transformed into a supply chain management enterprise and continued to achieve good performance, rising all the way. However, all this ended in 2020 annual report difficult birth, after in-depth investigation found that the so-called outstanding performance is just a phantom of the moon mirror flower. Surprisingly, Beijing Tianyuanquan Certified Public Accountants Co.,Ltd. issued a standard unqualified opinion in the first five years of the six-year fraud of Easy Visible.This case takes the development process of the huge fraud incident of Easy Visible as a clue, guides students to analyze the financial status of Easy Visible from the perspective of audit, and understands the types and motivations of financial fraud of Easy Visible. In addition, it lets students analyze how to identify audit risks. And with the help of the details of this incident, guide students how to use audit procedures to identify the financial fraud of enterprises and understand the key points of each link of substantive analysis procedures in the annual report audit, so as to enhance professional vigilance. After understanding the whole fraud incident, students will have a deeper understanding of the reasonable guarantee and independence requirements in the audit responsibility, and think about how to restrain the financial fraud of enterprises from the perspective of audit and supervision, and think about how to restrain the financial fraud of enterprises from the perspective of audit, and help to improve the market supervision on the fraud of listed companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计学》、《审计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务舞弊的类型及动因；企业审计风险评估；财务舞弊审计程序及实质性分析程序；注册会计师的审计责任；独立性的要求；提高审计质量的措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
